Third-party notices
-------------------

This distribution includes a stripped skeleton of Auth0's published Management
API OpenAPI specification at:

  api/auth0-management-api.openapi.json

Only the structural shape (paths, methods, parameters, and JSON-schema
definitions) is included; all Auth0-authored prose (descriptions, externalDocs
links, x-* extensions) has been removed by cmd/genopenapi/main.go before the
file was committed. The raw upstream document is gitignored and never
redistributed.

  Source: https://auth0.com/docs/api/management/openapi.json

