Bundled Go module dependencies
------------------------------

Release binaries (the goreleaser-produced archives + the Docker images) are
statically linked and include the third-party Go modules listed in `go.mod`,
under their respective licenses (MIT, BSD-2-Clause, BSD-3-Clause, Apache-2.0,
ISC, MPL-2.0). A machine-readable inventory ships alongside each release
archive as an SPDX-JSON Software Bill of Materials:

  <release-archive>.spdx.json

and a per-archive `THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md` aggregates each module's
copyright + license text. See `make sboms` / `make licenses` for how to
regenerate locally.
